&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have a positions available within our Dental Access Centre Nursing Team:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Dental Nurse, Full time 37.5 hours/week, Fixed-Term&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(Maternity Post)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;for 9 months; work plan will includeone out of hours session per week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome all applicants who meet the essential criteria for the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for experienced Dental Nurse to provide excellent support to the dental team within the Dental Access Centre. Dedicated to providing the smooth and efficient running of the surgery in providing a high standard of dental care to the patients exclusively NHS routine and urgent dental care to people of all ages including those varied special care/additional needs and those who have had difficulty accessing GDS NHS dental care at sites across Herefordshire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be able to travel across Herefordshire in the delivery of dental care.&lt;/p&gt;
